cast.overview: In 1800s England, a well-meaning but selfish young woman meddles in the love lives of her friends.
cast.title: Emma.

details.biography: Suzy Bloom is Miss Gilbert in 'EMMA' (Universal Pictures) directed by Autumn de Wilde, Catherine in 'The Art Of Love' (Netflix), Daisy in 'Sweet' (Angry Donkey) starring opposite Noel Fielding and Julian Barratt in this BAFTA nominated and award winning film. She is Patsy in Matt Berry and Rich Fulcher's 'Snuff Box' (BBC3) and Rachel in 'Genie In The House' - Nickelodeon's flagship sitcom.
details.name: Suzy Bloom
